# VMS template registry

Template file: `server/assets/template.docx` (local, gitignored). Tags use docxtemplater syntax.

When adding a VMS field, update **all** that apply:

1. Word template tags (e.g. `{candidate_first_name}`, `{#professional_experiences}...`)
2. `mapCandidateToTemplateData()` in `server/utils/docxBuilder.ts`
3. Intake UI + `candidates` schema/migrations if the field is user-collected

Unmapped template tags render blank — document known gaps in PR description.

Reference merged tags in `docxBuilder.ts`; do not use old `{first_name}` / `{#employers}` names.
